%% Doctor Authentication (Email + Password)
sequenceDiagram
  actor D as Doctor
  participant API as Next.js API
  participant DB as doctors
  participant MW as middleware.ts
  D->>API: POST /api/auth/doctor/login (email, password)
  API->>DB: Query doctors by email
  API->>API: Verify bcrypt hash
  alt Match
    API-->>D: JWT (role=doctor) in httpOnly cookie
    D->>MW: GET /dashboard
    MW-->>D: Allowed (role=doctor)
  else No match
    API-->>D: 401 Unauthorized
  end
